  <brief_title>S9628 Dexamethasone Plus Interferon Alfa in Treating Patients With Primary Systemic Amyloidosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Dexamethasone/Alpha-Interferon in AL Amyloidosis</official_title>
